{"tid":2131743,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【虛銀登場】匯立銀行正式開業 管理層：用戶資料全部留港","createTime":"2020-07-30T04:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T07:17:55.000Z","uid":44569,"like":6,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"571dae51b26892634cba4e425a77076a12f4d3c2","tid":2131743,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"港產虛擬銀行匯立銀行（ WeLab Bank）宣佈正式開業，目前推出兩項皇牌產品，分別是GoSave存款及設有高達8%簽賬現金回贈的記賬卡，管理層目標年底推出貸款服務，強調運用頂級科技確保資料加密及網絡安全，「用戶資料全部留港，不會轉移去其他地方」。<br />\n<br />\n匯立銀行推出初期暫設兩項產品，一是GoSave存款計劃，是香港首個以人數決定利率的定期存款產品，參加GoSave人數愈多，利率就愈高，年利率最高可達 4.5%，起存額低至10港元，隨時提款而亦無需額外費用，在期限內最多可提取2次；二是無卡號記賬卡，可用作消費或網購，亦可在全港的JETCO自動櫃員機提取現金,優惠期內憑卡消費更可享高達8%的現金回贈，符合現金回贈的交易金額上限為港幣3,000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200730/6DWZE4HPDEBUW2N3K6OOQYXB3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200730%2F6DWZE4HPDEBUW2N3K6OOQYXB3Q%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=bd600cb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200730%2F6DWZE4HPDEBUW2N3K6OOQYXB3Q%2F&h=52160697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200730/6DWZE4HPDEBUW2N3K6OOQYXB3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"c4a5e01b07c1f3aa7a043139192d454d65f35bc7","tid":2131743,"uid":204227,"like":122,"dislike":0,"score":122,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:57:33.000Z","msg":"依加嘅香港＝支那<br />\n留港＝留支<br />\n其實冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e745eb604c6be866a91ccf024c6c6e075aded4dc","tid":2131743,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"Welab冇中資咩？"},{"pid":"2f430049e8935fda93a9f1146928ad89dce4ae75","tid":2131743,"uid":73092,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"支資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c7209424a9d16d